parameters: Now’s not the time for this —
I need to find out what happened!
Maybe it's a dumb question, but...
are we really just going to leave that hole
I’ll take care of it later.
Don’t worry — leave it to me.
There’s one more thing bothering me...
Am I really going to sleep in this same bed
Eventually, you'll be moved to a more suitable
One where time will... stop for you.
Well... I just hope it’s just as comfy.
In that case, thanks for everything —
I guess I’ll see you... sometime soon?
I’ve got a bad feeling about this...
Guess I’m not falling asleep after all...
Hmmm... You really have been through a lot in such a
No wonder your mind’s racing and your brain waves are out
I’ll have to come up with something to clear your head
Wait... I think I’ve got it!
Not sure if you'll like it, though...
But hey, maybe it’s worth a try.
Give me a moment, I’ll be right back.
But since there's no one else around...
well, I usually fall asleep alone.
It’d be nice to have someone nearby, for a change.
I mean... you caught me off guard.
Where did that even come from?
I thought... sharing a bed might help you relax —
Isn’t that what you need right now?
Well, I mean... they’re definitely nice pajamas...
No one’s complimented me in ages...
I’ll help you relax and fall asleep peacefully.
There are more “pharmaceutical” ways to do that,
This is more natural — and I want what’s best for you.
Honestly... I’m kind of scared about what’s coming.
I know... I saw it in your eyes the moment you helped
And thank you again... I truly mean it.
I don’t know what would’ve happened.
Be here when I wake up. Please.
You don’t need to worry about that.
I just hope this helps you let go of your thoughts
Now come closer... I want to hold you.
Unless that’s a problem, of course...
In fact, I’d say... it’s a real comfort.
Take care of yourself, my friend!
